      <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-1">Docker Compose</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Multi-container local development with Docker Compose.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/docs/deployment/kubernetes" class="block p-4 bg-surface-800 rounded-lg border border-surface-600/50 hover:border-quantum-500/50 transition-colors">
      <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-1">Kubernetes</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Manual Kubernetes deployment with fine-grained control.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/docs/deployment/helm" class="block p-4 bg-surface-800 rounded-lg border border-surface-600/50 hover:border-quantum-500/50 transition-colors">
      <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-1">Helm Charts</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">One-command production deployment with Helm.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/docs/deployment/air-gapped" class="block p-4 bg-surface-800 rounded-lg border border-surface-600/50 hover:border-quantum-500/50 transition-colors">
