  <h2 id="api-reference" class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-4">API Reference</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">Complete API documentation for REST, gRPC, and authentication.</p>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
    <a href="/docs/api/rest-api" class="block p-4 bg-surface-800 rounded-lg border border-surface-600/50 hover:border-quantum-500/50 transition-colors">
      <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-1">REST API</h3>
